  </primary_outcome>
  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Clinical Laboratory Measures</measure>
    <time_frame>17 days</time_frame>
    <description>Safety and tolerability of oral administered ganaxolone vs. placebo as assessed by change from baseline in laboratory measures (biochemistry, hematology and urinalysis) per group and number of individuals with potentially clinically significant abnormal values of laboratory assessments in each group.</description>
